{
  "section_id": "05-tsmcs-supply-situation",
  "title": "TSMC’s Supply Situation",
  "title_translation": "台积电供应现状",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "id": "p000",
      "index": 0,
      "source": "With demand running far ahead of supply, TSMC is expanding capacity and pushing its existing lines to the limit, extracting every possible wafer from its nameplate capacity. As a result, effective N3 utilization is expected to exceed 100% in the second half of 2026. The company is also shifting certain process layers to other fabs to free up incremental N3 capacity wherever possible.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0038",
      "parent_block_index": 38,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
      "parent_block_markdown": "With demand running far ahead of supply, TSMC is expanding capacity and pushing its existing lines to the limit, extracting every possible wafer from its nameplate capacity. As a result, effective N3 utilization is expected to exceed 100% in the second half of 2026. The company is also shifting certain process layers to other fabs to free up incremental N3 capacity wherever possible.",
      "parent_block_plain_text": "With demand running far ahead of supply, TSMC is expanding capacity and pushing its existing lines to the limit, extracting every possible wafer from its nameplate capacity. As a result, effective N3 utilization is expected to exceed 100% in the second half of 2026. The company is also shifting certain process layers to other fabs to free up incremental N3 capacity wherever possible.",
      "parent_source_html": null,
      "parent_inline_elements": [],
      "segment_start": 0,
      "segment_end": 386,
      "expected_tokens": [],
      "format_recovery_status": "not_applicable",
      "format_errors": [],
      "is_heading": false,
      "heading_level": null,
      "heading_chain": [],
      "is_metadata": false,
      "metadata_type": null,
      "translations": {
        "pro": {
          "text": "在需求远超供给的背景下，台积电正在扩充产能，并将现有产线逼至极限，竭力从其铭牌产能中榨取每一片晶圆。因此，预计到2026年下半年，实际N3制程稼动率将突破100%。此外，台积电还将特定的工艺层转移至其他晶圆厂，以尽可能释放增量的N3制程产能。",
          "model": "pro",
          "created_at": "2026-03-13T22:44:54.719660",
          "tokenized_text": null,
          "format_issues": []
        },
        "manual": {
          "text": "当前需求远超供应，台积电正在扩充产能，并将现有产线逼至极限，力求从标称产能中榨取每一片晶圆。受此影响，预计2026年下半年N3的实际产能利用率将突破100%。此外，台积电还将特定工艺层转移至其他晶圆厂，尽一切可能释放额外的N3产能。",
          "model": "manual",
          "created_at": "2026-03-15T13:27:16.209436",
          "tokenized_text": null,
          "format_issues": []
        },
        "default": {
          "text": "当前需求远超供应，台积电（TSMC）正在扩充产能，并将现有产线逼至极限，力求从标称产能中榨取每一片晶圆。受此影响，预计2026年下半年N3的实际产能利用率将突破100%。此外，台积电还将特定工艺层转移至其他晶圆厂，尽一切可能释放额外的N3产能。",
